436
00:29:07,297 --> 00:29:08,534
Apologize to her right now.

437
00:29:08,803 --> 00:29:10,167
Why should I?

438
00:29:10,543 --> 00:29:12,110
Since I'm telling the truth.

439
00:29:16,333 --> 00:29:18,493
She's nothing but a nursemaid.

440
00:29:19,083 --> 00:29:20,767
