536
00:35:22,483 --> 00:35:24,039
You're shameless for asking more.

537
00:35:24,050 --> 00:35:27,174
How would we know
you didn't rip us off?

538
00:35:27,929 --> 00:35:30,200
You handled everything yourself.

539
00:35:30,589 --> 00:35:32,073
You could cover up anything.

540
00:35:32,410 --> 00:35:33,410
Right, ladies?

541
00:35:33,421 --> 00:35:34,421
- Yes.
- Yes.

542
00:35:34,657 --> 00:35:35,657
Let me.

543
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:40,207
If you rip us off even one penny,

544
00:35:40,463 --> 00:35:42,200
I'll report you and humiliate you.

545
00:35:44,382 --> 00:35:46,280
- Bu-nga!
- Since you're reporting me,

546
00:35:46,491 --> 00:35:48,667
report me for assaulting you too!

547
00:35:49,029 --> 00:35:50,906
You're just the mistresses

548
00:35:51,135 --> 00:35:53,560
my father supported
when he was alive.

549
00:35:53,743 --> 00:35:55,153
How much did you get?

550
00:35:55,389 --> 00:35:56,673
Don't think I don't know.

551
00:35:56,903 --> 00:35:58,120
You're lucky

552
00:35:58,403 --> 00:36:01,633
he was kind enough
to include you in his will.

553
00:36:01,923 --> 00:36:03,460
Let me tell you something.

554
00:36:03,857 --> 00:36:05,600
My father's fortune

555
00:36:05,683 --> 00:36:06,860
is partly my mother's!

556
00:36:07,542 --> 00:36:11,226
I'll consider it as a charity
for the animals my father kept!

557
00:36:11,482 --> 00:36:12,482
Bu-nga!

558
00:36:12,890 --> 00:36:13,996
You're crossing the line!

559
00:36:26,130 --> 00:36:27,130
Bu-nga!

560
00:36:30,223 --> 00:36:31,369
You think you're so good?

561
00:36:32,630 --> 00:36:34,816
What are you gonna do
to my master? No way!

562
00:36:34,883 --> 00:36:37,203
I always hated you.
I'll slap a lesson into you!

563
00:36:37,537 --> 00:36:39,000
No! No!

564
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,877
- Ms. Malai!
- Malai?

565
00:36:43,583 --> 00:36:44,752
You dared hurt my friend?

566
00:36:44,763 --> 00:36:45,980
Yeah! So what?!

567
00:36:50,029 --> 00:36:51,029
Let me go.

568
00:36:52,915 --> 00:36:53,975
Bu-nga!

569
00:37:00,330 --> 00:37:01,963
- Stop!
- Bu-nga! No!

570
00:37:02,442 --> 00:37:03,442
Bu-nga!

571
00:37:12,783 --> 00:37:13,783
Ms. Bu-nga!

572
00:37:16,639 --> 00:37:18,206
Enough, Bu-nga!

573
00:37:18,499 --> 00:37:19,499
Ms. Bu-nga!

574
00:37:20,466 --> 00:37:21,466
Bu-nga!

575
00:37:21,477 --> 00:37:22,477
Im, help me!

576
00:37:24,107 --> 00:37:25,570
- Ms. Bu-nga!
- Enough!

577
00:37:26,146 --> 00:37:28,287
- Bu-nga! Enough, Bu-nga!
- Ms. Bu-nga!

578
00:37:31,793 --> 00:37:33,086
Is there anyone here?!

579
00:37:33,593 --> 00:37:34,760
Drag them out of here!

580
00:37:42,210 --> 00:37:44,697
If you dare, report to the police.

581
00:37:45,210 --> 00:37:46,210
So I can expose you.

582
00:37:46,923 --> 00:37:50,317
You spent my father's money
on pampering another man.

583
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:54,197
You love gambling.

584
00:37:54,737 --> 00:37:56,397
You have a huge gambling debt.

585
00:37:57,630 --> 00:38:00,397
And you stole my mother's
things and sold them.

586
00:38:02,490 --> 00:38:04,307
If you want to come after me,

587
00:38:04,584 --> 00:38:06,417
prepare to be thrown in jail.

588
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:09,613
I'll take back
all my father's stuff from you!

589
00:38:10,297 --> 00:38:11,297
Do you want that?

590
00:38:13,403 --> 00:38:14,403
Leave!

591
00:38:20,009 --> 00:38:21,483
Not running your mouth anymore?

592
00:38:22,343 --> 00:38:23,636
Come on, Im.

593
00:38:24,883 --> 00:38:26,123
I'm glad they're leaving.

594
00:38:26,903 --> 00:38:28,950
They won't dare
come after Bu-nga again.

595
00:38:30,783 --> 00:38:32,113
Does it hurt bad, Malai?

596
00:38:32,663 --> 00:38:34,047
You took the slap for me.

597
00:38:35,148 --> 00:38:36,148
It's okay.

598
00:38:36,555 --> 00:38:38,188
I was shocked more than anything.

599
00:38:38,269 --> 00:38:41,280
From now on,
you'll get to live in peace.

600
00:38:43,036 --> 00:38:45,019
Let them try come after me again.

601
00:39:04,740 --> 00:39:07,920
I wish we didn't slip up
and let them hurt you, Ms. Malai.

602
00:39:08,383 --> 00:39:09,554
It's okay.

603
00:39:09,716 --> 00:39:10,800
It's nothing.

604
00:39:11,830 --> 00:39:12,830
Bu-nga,

605
00:39:13,016 --> 00:39:15,226
were you being too hard on them?

606
00:39:15,896 --> 00:39:18,333
That's why I wanted you
to try talking to them.

607
00:39:18,743 --> 00:39:20,640
I'm afraid those wicked women

608
00:39:20,775 --> 00:39:23,493
will come back and hurt Ms. Bu-nga.

609
00:39:23,748 --> 00:39:24,748
I don't care.

610
00:39:24,856 --> 00:39:26,340
When we face bad people,

611
00:39:26,350 --> 00:39:28,493
if we act weak, they'll bully us.

612
00:39:28,703 --> 00:39:31,053
We must fight back. It's justice.

613
00:39:31,969 --> 00:39:33,772
You should practice.

614
00:39:36,069 --> 00:39:37,554
I'm not as bold as you are.

615
00:39:38,609 --> 00:39:39,894
I'm scared just watching you.

616
00:39:40,636 --> 00:39:41,636
See?

617
00:39:41,977 --> 00:39:43,114
You're like this.

618
00:39:43,303 --> 00:39:46,047
That's why you're always
taken advantage of.

619
00:39:46,896 --> 00:39:50,334
Keep your goodness
for only good people.

620
00:39:50,636 --> 00:39:52,929
Because goodness
can't defeat bad people.

621
00:39:53,529 --> 00:39:56,220
If we're nice to them,
they'll think we stupid.

622
00:39:56,836 --> 00:39:57,836
Understood?

623
00:40:22,990 --> 00:40:24,727
That makes me miss her even more.

624
00:40:26,616 --> 00:40:28,616
Hurry and wake up, my dear friend.

625
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:30,807
I miss you so much.

626
00:40:31,463 --> 00:40:33,337
I miss her too, ma'am.

627
00:40:41,310 --> 00:40:42,310
Ms. Malai,

628
00:40:42,723 --> 00:40:44,256
someone's here to see you.

629
00:40:45,883 --> 00:40:46,883
Who is it?

630
00:40:47,083 --> 00:40:48,223
A servant called Dech.

631
00:40:51,677 --> 00:40:53,440
If you still
don't wanna see anyone,

632
00:40:53,563 --> 00:40:55,553
I can deal with him for you.

633
00:40:57,334 --> 00:40:58,334
Uh, yes.

634
00:40:58,689 --> 00:41:00,398
I don't wanna see anyone right now.

635
00:41:00,409 --> 00:41:01,409
Please deal with him.

636
00:41:01,735 --> 00:41:02,735
I will.

637
00:41:03,495 --> 00:41:06,550
Get another servant
to take Ms. Bu-nga to her room.

638
00:41:06,617 --> 00:41:07,617
I will.

639
00:41:08,703 --> 00:41:10,346
Don't worry, Ms. Malai.

640
00:41:11,029 --> 00:41:12,173
I'll deal with him.

641
00:41:13,462 --> 00:41:14,462
Thanks.

642
00:41:29,097 --> 00:41:30,097
Where's Ms. Malai?

643
00:41:30,397 --> 00:41:32,297
She's unable to receive anyone.

644
00:41:32,797 --> 00:41:34,994
She's taking care of Ms. Bu-nga.

645
00:41:35,290 --> 00:41:37,034
Was she informed
Dech asked to see her?

646
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:38,190
She was.

647
00:41:38,357 --> 00:41:40,914
She didn't want to see anyone.

648
00:41:41,090 --> 00:41:42,467
May I wait then?

649
00:41:42,617 --> 00:41:43,710
You may not.

650
00:41:43,963 --> 00:41:45,554
I'm really sorry.

651
00:41:45,671 --> 00:41:48,011
Ms. Malai really
doesn't want to see anyone.

652
00:42:58,390 --> 00:42:59,630
If you're really guilty,

653
00:43:00,097 --> 00:43:01,320
I can't help you.

654
00:43:16,822 --> 00:43:22,329
♪ Here's a heart
that's always faithful ♪

655
00:43:22,609 --> 00:43:27,219
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

656
00:43:28,281 --> 00:43:34,216
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

657
00:43:34,866 --> 00:43:38,383
♪ To you alone ♪

658
00:43:38,573 --> 00:43:44,379
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

659
00:43:44,600 --> 00:43:50,633
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

660
00:43:51,161 --> 00:43:53,834
♪ Whatever you want ♪

661
00:43:54,109 --> 00:43:58,753
♪ Everything I've done ♪

662
00:43:59,090 --> 00:44:01,373
♪ What's it for? ♪

663
00:44:01,427 --> 00:44:06,891
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

664
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:12,738
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

665
00:44:13,135 --> 00:44:18,633
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

666
00:44:18,930 --> 00:44:24,693
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪
